dct_description_sm: These vector maps represent all administrative boundary levels of France and the Departments and Communities Overseas from 2010. Included designations are: Regions, Departments, Arrondissements, Communes, and Cantons.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
